      <description>&lt;p&gt;Below are the instructions on how to get started. Please read carefully&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;If you have any issues contact us on Discord.&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;alert alert-danger clearfix&#34; role=&#34;alert&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;    &#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;float-start&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;svg aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; class=&#34;bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill hi-svg-inline alert-icon me-2&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; height=&#34;1em&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 16 16&#34; width=&#34;1em&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M8.982 1.566a1.13 1.13 0 0 0-1.96 0L.165 13.233c-.457.778.091 1.767.98 1.767h13.713c.889 0 1.438-.99.98-1.767zM8 5c.535 0 .954.462.9.995l-.35 3.507a.552.552 0 0 1-1.1 0L7.1 5.995A.905.905 0 0 1 8 5m.002 6a1 1 0 1 1 0 2 1 1 0 0 1 0-2&#34;/&gt;&#xA;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;alert-content&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;Please download and install &lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://mega.nz/file/w4EyGK5Q#Kbr5zlKhffrdtsBxLy3M4huotLMl6vKiLtO-LcRWFTQ&#34;&#xA;  &#xA;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;Ultima Online 9th Anniversary&lt;/a&gt; first. Make sure NOT to update it.&#xD;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;requirements&#34;&gt;Requirements&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;A fresh installed Ultima Online 9th anniversary edition that hasn&amp;rsquo;t been updated.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;A program that can open .zip files (Winzip, Winrar, 7-Zip etc&amp;hellip;)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;step-1&#34;&gt;Step 1&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Download our &lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://mega.nz/file/FpkVzAbQ#MSvnFcsEsNQFlPuwxmVk6yf9pug55H_2ZLF0gt6fdrY&#34;&#xA;  &#xA;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;shard files&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
